@startuml
title 用户登录时序图

actor Client as "前端页面"
participant API as "Django后端"
database DB as "SQLite数据库"

Client -> API: POST /api/user/login/
note right: {"username": "admin", "password": "xxx"}
API -> DB: 查询用户信息
DB --> API: 返回用户记录
API -> API: 验证密码哈希
alt 验证成功
    API --> Client: 200 OK
else 验证失败
    API --> Client: 401 Unauthorized
end

@enduml
